column4: Good omens: I saw a very large and vivid rainbow, and the KFC portents were good. Minor skipping on ``Day is Done'' prevented portents from being suspiciously perfect.
First day back after a week's leave.
First time at cinema since lockdown. Saw Tenet. (Awful.)
Felt a strong urge to pace up and down in the evening.
Gov announces South Yorkshire to go to Tier 3 from following Sat. I begin working from home.
Beautiful day in the snowy countryside around Wentworth Woodhouse,
Found out today that my B-hive contract would not be renewed.
